<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_323" id="161r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_323_r1l21">Vlm . <expan>Nordling<ex>en</ex></expan> / dinkelſpühell </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_323_r1l22">Hall / Heylprunn . <expan>Rot<ex>emburg</ex></expan> <expan>vvynſh<ex>eim</ex></expan> . </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_323_r1l23">weiſſemburg . / </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_323_r1l24"><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan> <expan>fr<ex>ewnde</ex></expan> Als vvir ew <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd gepeten heten / vns die <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>cʒeleih<ex>e</ex>n</expan></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_323_r1l25">vnd cʒu den <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> cʒeſchicken cʒu <expan>eine<ex>m</ex></expan> freuntlıchen tag auf den nechſten </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_323_r1l26">dinſtag gen Onelſpach / <expan>Laſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> wır <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> erſam <expan>freuntſch<ex>aft</ex></expan> <expan>vviſſe<ex>n</ex></expan> / daʒ vns </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_323_r1l27"><expan>d<ex>er</ex>ſelb</expan> tag <expan>wıd<ex>er</ex>boten</expan> vnd ab iſt / vnd iſt vns <expan>dieſ<ex>elb</ex></expan> botſchaft erſt als heint </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_323_r1l28">ſpate <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> / <expan>and<ex>er</ex>s</expan> wir <expan>het<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ew das ee cʒuvviſſen getan / <expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> ṽ <expan>p<ex>oſt</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_323_r1l29">Laurencij </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_323" id="161r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Ulm, <expan>Nordling<ex>en</ex></expan>, Dinkelspühell, Hall, Heylprunn,
                                <expan>Rot<ex>emburg</ex></expan>, <expan>Wynsh<ex>eim</ex></expan>,
                        Weissemburg</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, als wir ew
                                                  <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und
                                                gepeten heten, uns die <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>cze leih<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und czu den
                                                  <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> cze schicken czu
                                          <expan>eine<ex>m</ex></expan> freuntlichen tag <app><note><q type="date">auf
                                            den nechsten dinstag</q>18.08.1411</note></app> gen Onelspach,
                                                  <expan>lass<ex>en</ex></expan> wir
                                                  <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> ersam
                                                  <expan>freuntsch<ex>aft</ex></expan>
<expan>wisse<ex>n</ex></expan>, daz uns
                                                  <expan>d<ex>er</ex>selb</expan> tag
                                                  <expan>wid<ex>er</ex>boten</expan> und ab ist, und
                                                ist uns <expan>dies<ex>elb</ex></expan> botschaft
                                                erst als heint spate <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan>,
                                                  <expan>and<ex>er</ex>s</expan> wir
                                                  <expan>het<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ew das ee czuwissen
                                                getan. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> v
                                                  <expan>p<ex>ost</ex></expan> Laurencii.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
